DESIGN
======

A script runner should run only one script. If you want more scripts, just instantiate multiple runners
(with possibly differing time intervals).

params = {
    'script': 'RetrieveProcedureCountsPerQuarterScript',
    'script_params': {
        'study_name': 'ESPRESSO_v2.0_DPCA',
        'use_cache': true,
        'verbose': true,
        'output_dir': '/tmp/castor_dashboard',
        'output_json': 'histogram_dpca.json',
    },
}

